---
title: Chicken & Kale Harvest Salad with Apple & Honey Dijon Dressing
description: Step aside, side salad—this hearty kale version is the stuff of lunch dreams. We mix the tenderized greens with cooked chicken, apple slices, cabbage, and carrot, then we toss it with a creamy, tangy honey Dijon dressing and sprinkle it with chili flakes for a warming kick. This is a hearty-yet-light-feeling lunch idea you’re going to want to make even when it’s not harvest season.
